txt.en: 'Can you believe it? She's got her feet on my plate!'
'This song is nice enough, but I simply cannot enjoy it.'
'I wish she would stop standing on my plate.'
'I wish these musicians would move to some other table.'
'My food is ruined. Some people have no sense!'
'This would be a nice song if she was not standing in my supper!'
'This happened last time. Do you think these musicians do it on purpose?'
